<div class="about-container">
    <h1>About FlexTask</h1>
    <p>
        <strong>FlexTask</strong> is a modern, responsive To-Do List web application built with ASP.NET Core MVC, Entity Framework Core, and SQL Server LocalDB. The app is designed for personal productivity, portfolio projects, and learning full-stack development with .NET.
    </p>
    <h3>Key Features</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Clean and minimalist interface using CSS Flexbox</li>
        <li>Full CRUD operations for tasks</li>
        <li>Active and completed tasks are visually separated</li>
        <li>Responsive design for all devices</li>
        <li>Data persistence with MS SQL LocalDB</li>
    </ul>
    <h3>Technologies Used</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>ASP.NET Core MVC</li>
        <li>Entity Framework Core</li>
        <li>SQL Server LocalDB</li>
        <li>HTML5, CSS3 (Flexbox)</li>
    </ul>
    <h3>Developer</h3>
    <p>
        This project was created for educational and portfolio purposes. For questions or feedback, please contact the developer.
    </p>
</div>
